Package net.didion.jwnl.dictionary Description

Classes for acessing dictionary information. The two classes of Dictionary included with JWNL are FileBackedDictionary - which looks up information in text files (usually the files provided with the WordNet distribution), and MapBackedDictionary - which looks up information in in-memory tables (or Maps).
